org.eclipse.persistence.services.websphere

Class WebSphereRuntimeServices

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.persistence.services.RuntimeServices
      • org.eclipse.persistence.services.websphere.WebSphereRuntimeServices
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MBeanWebSphereRuntimeServices

    public class WebSphereRuntimeServices
extends RuntimeServices

    Purpose: Provide a dynamic interface into the EclipseLink Session.

    Description: This class is meant to provide facilities for managing an EclipseLink session external to EclipseLink over JMX.

    Since:
    EclipseLink 2.1.1
